descp2: The output stream, logging level, or file to print to. Defaults to sys.stderr, but sys.stdout, tf.compat.v1.logging.info, tf.compat.v1.logging.warning, tf.compat.v1.logging.error, absl.logging.info, absl.logging.warning and absl.loogging,error are also supported. To print to a file, pass a string started with "file://" followed by the file path, e.g., "file:///tmp/foo.out".
